{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very familiar-- and this cousin of my who-- who made this partisan, you know, a group-- he knew, very well, the forest.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- at first, during summer, we had like, like out of a-- like the soldiers have the-- the fabric that they make the-- how you call-- that we can-- you know, when it rains, or something, that we could sleep there and we could, you know-- during summer was OK.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How you call the-- oh, gosh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tents.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He made a tent, a big, big tent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were, I think, about 30 people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with food was a problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to go down to the-- to the village, to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of the gentiles, you know, they were Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This-- this village was Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, even some didn't like Jews, but they were also prosecuted from the Ukrainians, because they were-- they hated the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they tried to help us out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they tried-- a few of the men, sometimes-- I used to be the guide, you know, to take them-- because I knew the village-- and to buy some food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whatever you could-- bread, and this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a lot of times, all these-- the young boys, they just went and they-- they-- they just went into some villages, and went in to-- to-- to farmers, and they just took things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just-- how would you say, not a holdup-- but, you know, they just, you know, whatever they could find there, they just took.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because we had nothing to lose and we had nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But mostly, we tried to-- to get from them, to buy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We still had a little money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't remember how and what, but we still had.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
